Citation.sTitle: Speed of Sound in Propan-1-ol + Heptane Mixtures under Elevated Pressures
Citation.sAbstract: The speed of sound in propan-1-ol + heptane mixtures was measured over the whole composition range within the temperatures from 293.15 K to 318.15 K and at pressures up to 120 MPa. The effect of pressure and temperature on the speed of sound has been discussed.
